ried out coherently\nin a Bayesian framework. We also conduct an extensive simulation study and\napply our model to a real, SO2 pollution data over Europe. The results are\nhighly encouraging.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 May 2014 10:27:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2016 03:27:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 24 Aug 2017 13:49:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-25"}
